OL,3,CViolent and abusive behaviour towards
OL,4,Croad workers has become 'part of the
OL,5,Cjob'
OL,7,FWatch Lauren Hall's investigation into
OL,8,Fthe abuse of road workers across the UK
OL,10,FAn investigation carried out by ITV
OL,11,FNews has found road workers are
OL,12,Froutinely experiencing abuse from
OL,13,Fmembers of the public.
OL,15,FThis includes being shouted at, sworn
OL,16,Fat and having objects thrown at them,
OL,17,Fas well as being physically attacked
OL,18,Fand threatened with weapons.
