OL,3,CViolent and abusive behaviour towards
OL,4,Croad workers has become 'part of the
OL,5,Cjob'
OL,7,FWe surveyed more than 250 road workers
OL,8,Fand traffic officers and found a third
OL,9,Fhad experienced violence. One road
OL,10,Fworker we spoke to, who has asked not
OL,11,Fto be identified, described an
OL,12,Fincident when a driver got out of his
OL,13,Fvehicle and approached her patrol car.
OL,15,F"He managed to get the doors open and
OL,16,Fhe come in with his fist raised," she
OL,17,Fremembers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
