OL,7,F"I lent over towards my colleague to
OL,8,Fget out of the way and my feet went
OL,9,Fout the door, and he decided to then
OL,10,Fslam the door which cut my ankle and
OL,11,Ffractured a bone in my ankle joint."
OL,13,FNearly all the road workers and
OL,14,Ftraffic officers we surveyed have
OL,15,Fexperienced verbal abuse and well over
OL,16,Fhalf have been threatened with
OL,17,Fviolence.
