OL,4,Croad workers has become 'part of the
OL,5,Cjob'
OL,7,FMarc Woodall, a Contract Director
OL,8,Frunning projects at Balfour Beatty,
OL,9,Ftold us about a recent incident: "Only
OL,10,Fin the last week in East Sussex we had
OL,11,Fan incident where we had a road
OL,12,Fclosure in place, a member of the
OL,13,Fpublic was a bit frustrated by that
OL,14,Fand wanted to get through," he said.
OL,16,F"Obviously, as is right, our member of
OL,17,Fstaff refused that individual entry
OL,18,Fand, when that happened, that member
OL,19,Fof the public actually pulled a knife
OL,20,Fand physically and verbally threatened
OL,21,Fthat member of staff."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
