OL,3,CViolent and abusive behaviour towards
OL,4,Croad workers has become 'part of the
OL,5,Cjob'
OL,7,FOur survey found more than a quarter
OL,8,Fof road workers were subjected to
OL,9,Fabuse most days, while another quarter
OL,10,Fface it at least once a week.
OL,12,FRoad signs discouraging abusive
OL,13,Fbehaviour are now often used at sites
OL,14,Fwhere there are roadworks. Some sites
OL,15,Fare also using CCTV and traffic
OL,16,Fofficers at National Highways now wear
OL,17,Fbody cameras, but they are still
OL,18,Fexperiencing regular abuse from
OL,19,Fmembers of the public.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
