OL,5,Cjob'
OL,7,FWe joined two traffic officers out on
OL,8,Fpatrol who explained it is a daily
OL,9,Foccurrence.
OL,11,F"If you spoke to most traffic
OL,12,Fofficers, most of them experience some
OL,13,Fkind of abuse every day," said Antony
OL,14,FPhipps who has been in the role for a
OL,15,Fnumber of years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
