OL,3,CViolent and abusive behaviour towards
OL,4,Croad workers has become 'part of the
OL,5,Cjob'
OL,7,FHis colleague Sian Plant agrees and
OL,8,Fsays she feels it has become part of
OL,9,Fthe job: "Unfortunately I think it
OL,10,Fhas. You just kind of accept it which
OL,11,Fisn't ok. I understand that drivers
OL,12,Fare frustrated but, at the end of the
OL,13,Fday, I'm just doing my job, and so is
OL,14,Feveryone else."
OL,16,FNearly a quarter of those we surveyed
OL,17,Ftold us that the abuse they experience
OL,18,Fhas made them consider leaving their
OL,19,Fjob.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
