OL,7,FA national summit was held in
OL,8,FManchester on Tuesday to raise
OL,9,Fawareness of the issue, as part of
OL,10,FRespect our Workforce week.
OL,12,FIt was organised by Kevin Robinson who
OL,13,Fruns Stamp it Out. This national
OL,14,Fcampaign was set up to tackle the
OL,15,Fabuse of road workers.
OL,17,FHe explained why he feels it is more
OL,18,Fimportant than ever: "Obviously there
OL,19,Fis massive investment in the road
OL,20,Fnetwork at the moment," he said.
